{"type":"message","id":"4bb828f2","parentId":"c13aaa1d","timestamp":"2026-02-20T08:36:35.823Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_eqf32ma0qpxu_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-eastmoney\">东方财富</span>2026-02-19</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">两部门：加强烟花爆竹\"产储运销\"和燃放全链条安全管控</h3>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">两部门联合发文，要求加强烟花爆竹\"产储运销\"和燃放全链条安全管控。及时消除违规燃放、人员聚集等安全隐患，引导群众\"定时定点\"有序燃放。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">湖北宜城烟花爆竹爆燃事故致12人遇难</h3>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">湖北宜城发生烟花爆竹爆燃事故致12人遇难，其中7名成年人、5名未成年人，1人为经营者。安全生产再次敲响警钟。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-19</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">深港双城记：年轻人如何\"赚两边的钱\"？</h3>\n                <p class=\"news-summary\">深港双城记持续演绎，年轻人积极寻找两地投资和就业机会。跨境金融、创新科技领域合作为年轻人提供更多发展空间。</p>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"section\">\n            <h2 class=\"section-title\">📊 数据来源</h2>\n            <p style=\"color: #666; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8;\">\n                <span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span> yicai.com<br>\n                <span class=\"source-tag source-eastmoney\">东方财富</span> eastmoney.com<br>\n                <span class=\"source-tag source-163\">网易财经</span"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1771576595820}}
{"type":"message","id":"baaa9094","parentId":"4bb828f2","timestamp":"2026-02-20T08:36:59.899Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The file was truncated. I need to fix it by appending the missing closing tags and the footer. Let me fix this.","thinkingSignature":"e67ecdf2b2f9f2789f2c0b90aa3903baf02c6d2f77c3191fbfd48cd5f535c9a4"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_752lxckaq8w5_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/a-stock-news-report-2026-02-20.html","newText":"        <div class=\"section\">\n            <h2 class=\"section-title\">📊 数据来源</h2>\n            <p style=\"color: #666; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8;\">\n                <span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span> yicai.com<br>\n                <span class=\"source-tag source-eastmoney\">东方财富</span> eastmoney.com<br>\n                <span class=\"source-tag source-163\">网易财经</span> money.163.com<br>\n                <span class=\"source-tag source-sina\">新浪财经</span> finance.sina.com.cn<br>\n                <span class=\"source-tag source-10jqka\">同花顺</span> 10jqka.com.cn\n            </p>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"footer\">\n            <p>🤖 由 OpenClaw 自动生成 · 仅供参考，投资需谨慎</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>","oldText":"        <div class=\"section\">\n            <h2 class=\"section-title\">📊 数据来源</h2>\n            <p style=\"color: #666; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8;\">\n                <span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span> yicai.com<br>\n                <span class=\"source-tag source-eastmoney\">东方财富</span> eastmoney.com<br>\n                <span class=\"source-tag source-163\">网易财经</span"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":48542,"output":412,"cacheRead":11139,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60093,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":17715765